title: GSMC Relationship Podcast Episode 111 Dont Be So Shy (05-31-18)
content: John talks about how to prepare yourself for getting out there and meeting someone interesting and available for you.tips on staying positive how to be in group conversations or individuals, and how to use the interaction to give you clues as to if this person is a good fit for you.   As always, if you enjoyed the show, follow us and subscribe to the show you can find us on iTunes or on any app that carries podcasts as well as YouTube. Please remember to subscribe and give us a nice review. That way you’ll always be among the first to get the latest GSMC Relationship Podcasts.
